    <briefdescription>
<para><ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1FlexLayoutParams" kindref="compound">FlexLayoutParams</ref> stores per-child layout parameters for <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1FlexLayout" kindref="compound">FlexLayout</ref>. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This handle provides direct access to flex grow, shrink, basis, and align-self attached to a child view. Use <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1View_1a772712edaeac7bad4b3c19632394d336" kindref="member">View::SetLayoutParams()</ref> to attach parameters to a child view.</para>
